matrix <- bcell_mat["Fcrl5",]
matrix[1:5]
## AAACCCACAGTAGTGG-1 AAACCCAGTATACGGG-1 AAACGCTGTAGACAGC-1 AAAGAACAGCTTGTGT-1 
##           1.106459           1.050664           1.498928           0.000000 
## AAAGAACTCCTGCTAC-1 
##           1.049516
new_order <- order(matrix, decreasing = FALSE)

reduced <- bcell_tsne[new_order,]
reduced[1:5,]
matrix <- matrix[new_order]

df <- data.frame(dim_1 = reduced$dim_1, dim_2 = reduced$dim_2, exp = matrix)

ggplot(data = df, aes(x = dim_1, y = dim_2, color = exp)) + geom_point() +
    xlab("Dim_1") +
    ylab("Dim_2") +
    scale_colour_gradient(low = "gray88", high = "red" ) + labs(color = "Fcrl5")  +
    theme(text = element_text(size=15), 
          panel.grid.major = element_blank(), panel.grid.minor = element_blank(),
          panel.background = element_blank(), axis.line = element_line(colour = "black")) + ggtitle("Old0 + Young0") + ylim(0,30) +xlim(15,31)
